gism', 'The use of idelalisib with other potentially hepatotoxic agents such as azole antifungal agents, macrolide antibiotics, nefazodone, ritonavir, and telithromycin should be avoided whenever possible.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/176425/', '', 'Micafungin, Amphotericin B, Miconazole, Oteseconazole, Flucytosine, Anidulafungin', 'Futibatinib, Trametinib, Nintedanib, Afatinib, Dacomitinib, Tivozanib, Alectinib, Binimetinib', 1767369485);
